metadata.name: #01 .  A Baby Turtle
metadata.description:
A 3d representation of a small sea turtle that I found on the coast of the gulf of Mexico, it was part of a group of newborns, it was very small these days it must be enormous.
It is an endangered species, due to the consumption of its eggs, fortunately the native people have done a good job in the preservation and care.


By RoBot
